@startuml
skin rose
title Login Flow
actor User
participant "Next.js Client" as Client
participant "Login Server Action" as Action
participant "Supabase Client" as Supabase
participant "Next.js Middleware" as Middleware

User -> Client: Submit login form
activate Client
Client -> Action: login(email, password)
activate Action
Action -> Supabase: auth.signInWithPassword()
activate Supabase
Supabase --> Action: session tokens & user data
deactivate Supabase
Action -> Action: Set auth cookies
Action --> Client: redirect('/')
deactivate Action

note over Client: Page navigation triggered
Client -> Middleware: Request to protected route
activate Middleware
Middleware -> Supabase: auth.getUser()
activate Supabase
Supabase --> Middleware: user data
deactivate Supabase
Middleware --> Client: Allow access
deactivate Middleware
Client --> User: Display protected content
deactivate Client
@enduml